snippet.title: [TAS] Metal Gear Solid: VR Missions "100%" in 2:10:12.43
snippet.description: Metal Gear Solid: VR Missions (Special Missions in Europe) contains 300 action-packed levels with enough scintillating Snake-sneaking setpieces to last a lifetime. Originally a part of Integral, the 1999 Japanese re-release of Metal Gear Solid, it received a 2000 standalone release in North America and Europe as an extra bonus to satisfy fans hungry for more tactical espionage action. Watch as theenglishman sneaks, shoots, punches and investigates his way past the world leaderboards, all just to see a low-resolution piece of concept art from a game that came out twelve years ago.
